title: Narrative

* This example tests the ''priority'' between `toc-branchTemplate` and `toc-itemTemplate`

* Tiddler `bb` has `toc-branchTemplate: branch-tmpl` — applies to all children

* Tiddler `bb-bb` has `toc-itemTemplate: node-tmpl` — overrides the branch template for this node only

* `bb-bb-bb` should use the branch template (inherited from `bb`)

* `toc-itemTemplate` takes ''precedence'' over `toc-branchTemplate`

